====Usage notes====
In Chinese, {{zh-l|是}} cannot be used to mean ''to be'' if it is followed by an adjective. In those case, 是 is replaced by 很. Depending on the context, it will be translated to ''is very'' or simply to ''to be''.
{{zh-usex|他 很 高兴。|He is (very) happy}}

